#################### Ubuntu22 Preconfig @@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@

This autoinstall file is based on our Ubuntu 22 Preconfig script and targets single-server/ZFS deployments. 

The primary functionality of this script is as follows:

-Root user enabled with password hash of "password".
-SSH using root user and password.
-Installs listed packages (Houston modules, ZFS, Samba, NFS).
-Sets NetworkManager as primary networking tool.
-Enables Cockpit, installs firewalld, disables ufw, and creates firewall rule for Cockpit.
-Updates/Upgrades system.

For more information on deployment methods, consult this guide: http://192.168.1.91/doku45/doku.php?id=service:serv-ts-_testing_headless_rocky_install:network
